<L>__{interior kinograph studios george's dressing room day}
<D>__{in his dressing room, wearing a tailcoat and top hat, george is finishing putting his make up on. he has a white face and dark lips and eyes. his chauffeur is signing autographs for him on full length photographs of himself (george) with his dog. george says to him: title card: go and buy a piece of jewelry for my wife. a nice piece, to make it up to her. the chauffeur nods. having finished his mask up, george, picks up a photo, looks at it closely and then writes on it. as he leaves the dressing room, we see the photograph. he's written woof woof on it, and signed it with the paw print of a dog.}
